This is the location of the supporting files for my Ansible automation series on YouTube and their related blog posts.
https://www.youtube.com/@SkillNuggets
http://richardkilleen.co.uk/blog/

Contained in the lab files are the lab lessions which contain the playbooks, inventorys that i have used and the senario workbooks.

Lab 1 - Basics of installing ansible and running our first playbook
Lab 2 - Addinging interface descriptions and MGMT static routing
Lab 03 - Adding loopback interface and ip addressing, adding phyical interface addressing, descriptions and no shut
Lab 04 - Ensuring all routers have NTP configured and configuring a Ubuntu server for NTP
